title: Indeed.com's Sinclair Sees Discontent in Labor Market (Audio)
itunes:title: Indeed.com's Sinclair Sees Discontent in Labor Market (Audio)
description:
(Bloomberg) -- Taking Stock with Pimm Fox and Matt Miller. GUEST: Tara Sinclair, Chief Economist at Indeed.com, on the jobs numbers and a recent report uncovering worker discontent in the US despite a strong job market.
